{"word":"ἐπίφορος","slug":"ἐπίφορος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπίφορος</b></el> <el>(ἐπίφορος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐπιφέρω'><el>ἐπιφέρω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>carrying towards</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <i>favourable</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of ground, <i>sloping</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>near the time of bringing forth</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}